  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Increase in vehicular accidents due to illegal sand smugglers in Jharkhand",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that the vehicle carrying sand illegally caused an accident with a bus owned by the Sri Lanka Transport Board and a private bus and fled the scene.",
        "The incident took place today at 5 am on Sunday morning in the Mandigai area of \u200b\u200bBarutthura Road, Jaffna.",
        "A similar type of vehicle loaded with sand in an illegal manner lost speed and ran away from a private bus which was waiting to get diesel and ran away from there.",
        "After the police was informed about the accident, the police started investigations.",
        "Meanwhile, last week, a tipper vehicle carrying sand illegally drove into the crowd of devotees participating in the Nelliadi Mala Market Pilliyar temple festival and ran away. 7 people were injured in it.",
        "It is noted that the number of accidents due to illegal sand smugglers is increasing in Vadamaratshi areas."
      ],
